comments: Barnes (SAC) establishes himself in Mays (POR) path and marginal contact occurs as the two come together during Barnes' roll toward the basket.
Sharpe (POR) makes marginal contact with Monk's (SAC) right arm after the release, which does not affect his ability to return to the floor naturally.
Huerter (SAC) and Camara (POR) come together away from the ball and the contact is marginal.
Camara (POR) firms up in Sabonis' (SAC) path and does not deliver illegal contact when setting the screen.
Monk (SAC) momentarily places rests his hand from Mays' (POR) left shoulder during the drive and the marginal contact dissolves shortly thereafter.
Monk (SAC) moves alongside Mays' (POR) path and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Sabonis (SAC) firms up over his right leg and marginal contact occurs as Camara (POR) navigates around the screen.
Camara (POR) wraps his left arm around Sabonis' (SAC) waist and the illegal contact affects his ability to roll after setting the pick.
Sabonis (SAC) aligns along Mays' (POR) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive along the baseline.
Mitchell (SAC) and Grant (POR) come together while pursuing the loose ball and the contact is marginal.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Grant (POR) dribbles the ball off of his leg and the ball bounces out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to Sacramento.
Sabonis (SAC) firms up over his left foot and marginal contact occurs as Sharpe (POR) defends over the pick.
Ayton (POR) legally contests Monk's (SAC) driving shot attempt.
Huerter (SAC) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard an opponent.
Sharpe (POR) steps his left foot back and out of bounds while he is in contact with the ball. Possession is properly awarded to Sacramento.
Barnes (SAC) moves into Sharpe's (POR) space and initiates body contact that dislodges the defender during the rebounding opportunity.
Sharpe (POR) and Sabonis (SAC) come together away from the ball and the contact is marginal.
Ayton (POR) firms up over his left foot and marginal contact occurs as Edwards (SAC) defends over the pick.
Sabonis (SAC) jumps vertically as he retreats his arms into a vertical position and he absorbs the marginal contact with Mays (POR) during the driving shot attempt.
Sabonis (SAC) firms up over his left leg and marginal contact occurs as Sharpe (POR) defends over the screen.
Sabonis (SAC) firms up in Sharpe's (POR) path and marginal contact occurs as the two players come together during the pick.

After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of an offensive foul on Sharpe (POR) is overturned to a shooting foul.  Sharpe does not establish himself in a legal guarding position outside of the restricted area before contact occurs with Monk (SAC).
Camara (POR) and Edwards (SAC) come together at the same spot on the floor and the contact during the inbound is marginal.
Mitchell (SAC) legally contests Mays' POR) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Ellis (SAC) rests his forearm on Camara's (POR) side as the two players move together toward the loose ball and the contact is marginal.

Camara (POR) legally brings his hand to the ball and slides it off as Ellis (SAC) gathers the ball in two hands. The contact with the ball occurs prior to Ellis' upward shooting motion and the game clock expires prior to the release of the shot attempt.
Sabonis (SAC) lowers his arms and initiates contact with Ayton's (POR) head, which affects his jump shot attempt.
Thybulle (POR) cleanly deflects the ball prior to the contact to Sabonis' (SAC) body during the rebound, which is marginal.
Thybulle (POR) cleanly deflects the ball from Monk (SAC) as he attempts to retrieve the incoming pass.
Mitchell (SAC) deflects the ball from Grant (POR) during his drive in transition.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Mitchell (SAC) throws the ball off Grant (POR) who is last to touch the ball prior to it going out of bounds.
Sabonis (SAC) maintains his pivot foot prior to releasing his pass.
Monk (SAC) gets drawn in the air and makes contact with Camara's (POR) body, which is marginal and does not affect his SQBR.
Sabonis (SAC) cleanly dislodges the ball from Camara (POR) during his shot attempt near the basket.
Grant (POR) moves laterally into Sabonis (SAC) and makes contact to his body that affects his post shot attempt.
Grant (POR) engages and disengages with Edwards (SAC) as he attempts to get to the inbounds pass.
Ayton (POR) establishes himself in Edwards's (SAC) path and absorbs the incoming contact during the pick.
Edwards (SAC) moves alongside Grant's (POR) path and makes slight contact to his body, which is marginal during the driving shot attempt.
Ayton (POR) briefly grasps Sabonis' (SAC) jersey during the rebound and does not affect his FOM.
Monk (SAC) slightly extends his arm into Camara's (POR) body at the start of the drive, which does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position.
Ayton (POR) briefly grasps Sabonis' (SAC) arm, which does not affect his ability to pursue the rebound.
Camara (POR) commits a take foul on Monk (SAC).
Mitchell (SAC) avoids making contact with Grant (POR) during his upward shooting motion.
Mays (POR) establishes a screening position not in Mitchell's (SAC) path as the contact is marginal during the screen.
Mitchell (SAC) legally contests Grant's (POR) jump shot attempt.
